{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/blog/2015-06-04-saenai-no-hp-no-sotate-kaata/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"少年读书隙中窥月"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"c6b25f9b-9cc2-5031-8d04-acba31d869e0","excerpt":"上一版的主页做了也快一年了，前两天心血来潮，于是又做了一个新版本。这个版本融合了《大春物》和《不起眼女主角的育成方法》的相关要素，比如下边的这个和这个：   整个页面比较麻烦的部分在于 canvas…","html":"<p>上一版的主页做了也快一年了，前两天心血来潮，于是又做了一个新版本。这个版本融合了《大春物》和《不起眼女主角的育成方法》的相关要素，比如下边的这个和这个：</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/972a176cd4b01e45c6189ffdef074c76/b17f8/mv-sequel.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 38.513513513513516%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"mv-sequel\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/972a176cd4b01e45c6189ffdef074c76/1c72d/mv-sequel.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/972a176cd4b01e45c6189ffdef074c76/a80bd/mv-sequel.jpg 148w,\n/static/972a176cd4b01e45c6189ffdef074c76/1c91a/mv-sequel.jpg 295w,\n/static/972a176cd4b01e45c6189ffdef074c76/1c72d/mv-sequel.jpg 590w,\n/static/972a176cd4b01e45c6189ffdef074c76/a8a14/mv-sequel.jpg 885w,\n/static/972a176cd4b01e45c6189ffdef074c76/fbd2c/mv-sequel.jpg 1180w,\n/static/972a176cd4b01e45c6189ffdef074c76/b17f8/mv-sequel.jpg 1600w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/9bc853da8e937cb7c1a64763ba2dc7d5/eea4a/oregairu.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.08108108108109%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"oregairu\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/9bc853da8e937cb7c1a64763ba2dc7d5/1c72d/oregairu.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/9bc853da8e937cb7c1a64763ba2dc7d5/a80bd/oregairu.jpg 148w,\n/static/9bc853da8e937cb7c1a64763ba2dc7d5/1c91a/oregairu.jpg 295w,\n/static/9bc853da8e937cb7c1a64763ba2dc7d5/1c72d/oregairu.jpg 590w,\n/static/9bc853da8e937cb7c1a64763ba2dc7d5/a8a14/oregairu.jpg 885w,\n/static/9bc853da8e937cb7c1a64763ba2dc7d5/fbd2c/oregairu.jpg 1180w,\n/static/9bc853da8e937cb7c1a64763ba2dc7d5/eea4a/oregairu.jpg 1280w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>整个页面比较麻烦的部分在于 canvas 路径的绘制，为了绘制出正确的花形（这个词感觉哪里不对），狠狠地复习了一下解析几何的知识，并对 Javascript 的 Math 库的几个函数进行了充分的理解与运用。目前的代码就是单纯地绘制，如果以后有精力的话还可以做出像《未闻花名》ED 中的那种下落效果，就是代码会比较复杂，要考虑重绘，还要考虑路径对象的生成与销毁。</p>\n<p>字体方面，鉴于 Light 字重的汉字字体不是随处都有的，而用路径绘制又太麻烦，最后用的是图片。为了防止次级像素造成的边缘锯齿问题，使用了 2x 缩小的底图，把麻烦的锅交给浏览器了。从观察到的效果上还不错。</p>\n<p>和我做的别的一些页面一样，此次制作过程中也参考了别家的作品，再次感谢 Evan You （<a href=\"http://evanyou.me/\">http://evanyou.me/</a> ）的创意启发。</p>\n<p>P.S. 下单买了一大堆 PC 升级的配件，除了 CPU 和电源之外别的都换了，虽然初衷是装黑苹果吧……</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"冴えない HP の育てかた","publish_date":"2015-06-04T23:20:44.000+08:00","revise_date":"2015-06-04T23:20:44.000+08:00","draft":false}}},"pageContext":{"previous":{"id":"66e44f1a-03c7-5068-8e9e-38628c10bc21","fields":{"slug":"/blog/2015-05-04-big-world-little-freedom/","type":"blog","timeToRead":{"words":641,"minutes":4}},"frontmatter":{"title":"世界那么大，自由度却很小","publish_date":"2015-05-04T01:58:13.000+08:00"}},"slug":"/blog/2015-06-04-saenai-no-hp-no-sotate-kaata/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["1330398833","2356112386"],"slicesMap":{}}